<item>
            <title>[LU-17693] Inquiry: Coexistence of Minor Lustre Versions (2.15.2 and 2.15.4) in the Same System</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17693</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have a quick question: Is it possible for Lustre versions 2.15.2 (RHEL8.7) and 2.15.4 (RHEL8.9) to operate simultaneously within the same Lustre system? Specifically, could some OSS servers run version 2.15.4 (RHEL8.9) while others maintain version 2.15.2 (RHEL8.7)? Would this setup lead to any compatibility issues?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Jane&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
